    "patch_code": "private Set<String> keys(Object obj) {\n  Set<String> set = new HashSet<>();\n  try {\n    Field[] fields = obj.getClass().getDeclaredFields();\n    for (Field field : fields) {\n      String name = field.getName();\n      set.add(name);\n    }\n  } catch (Exception e) {\n    System.err.println(\"error:\" + e.getMessage());\n  }\n  return set;\n}",
